Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.16,0:00:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Regular\fs15\bord1\shad1\an8\b0}"干杯酒吧"\N- 始于1895年 -
Dialogue: 1,0:00:05.30,0:00:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}晚安 丹恩 回家路上注意安全
Dialogue: 1,0:00:13.64,0:00:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}那人唠叨得你耳朵都起茧了吧 教练
Dialogue: 1,0:00:17.19,0:00:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}是啊 但他人实在很不错 你知道吗？
Dialogue: 1,0:00:20.32,0:00:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}他是我第一个亲眼见到的乘坐过"泰坦尼克号"的人
Dialogue: 1,0:00:24.90,0:00:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}- 他是"泰坦尼克号"的幸存者？ - 我忘了问了
Dialogue: 1,0:00:30.33,0:00:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}教练 你为什么不叫我？这故事我怎么能错过
Dialogue: 1,0:00:32.91,0:00:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}我还以为你听过这个故事\N一艘大船 撞上冰山 邦的一声就沉了
Dialogue: 1,0:00:39.17,0:00:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}以后再听到有趣的故事 一定要叫上我\N这是酒保的乐趣来的
Dialogue: 1,0:00:44.63,0:00:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}你想听有趣的？泰坦尼克号算什么 过来
Dialogue: 1,0:00:48.26,0:00:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}格伦 把你刚才告诉我的再对他讲一遍
Dialogue: 1,0:00:51.89,0:00:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Regular\fs13\bord1\shad1\an8\b0}【大宝藏】NBC电视台1959-1973年播出的一部西部题材的长篇剧集
Dialogue: 1,0:00:51.89,0:00:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}我能把《大宝藏》的主题曲一字不差地唱出来
Dialogue: 1,0:00:58.27,0:00:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}唱吧 给山姆也听听
Dialogue: 1,0:00:59.86,0:01:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}我们打起架来啥都不怕呀 大宝藏！
Dialogue: 1,0:01:04.19,0:01:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}谁敢打我们中的任何一个 就得和我们全体打
Dialogue: 1,0:01:08.49,0:01:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}我们都是男子汉 个个不好惹 大宝藏！
Dialogue: 1,0:01:11.95,0:01:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}我们的人找茬打架 大伙儿都挺他
Dialogue: 1,0:01:15.79,0:01:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}我为人人 人人为我 说话就算话
Dialogue: 1,0:01:19.83,0:01:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}我为人人 人人为我
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.06,0:01:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnDFKai-SB\fs14\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}《干杯酒吧》\N第一季第20集 "唯有孤单最销魂"
Dialogue: 1,0:01:53.16,0:01:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Regular\fs16\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}中文字幕译制\Na7l9x1jl6
Dialogue: 1,0:02:36.28,0:02:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}- 球迷们好  - 诺姆！
Dialogue: 1,0:02:39.62,0:02:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}- 想来点什么？ - 名誉、财富、浪女
Dialogue: 1,0:02:42.83,0:02:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}是吗？来杯啤酒怎么样？
Dialogue: 1,0:02:44.75,0:02:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}自然更好
Dialogue: 1,0:02:47.25,0:02:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}工作找得怎样了？
Dialogue: 1,0:02:49.34,0:02:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}好消息 诸位 本人不再找工作了
Dialogue: 1,0:02:54.68,0:02:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}哥现在是跪求一份工作
Dialogue: 1,0:03:02.77,0:03:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}- 我简直不敢相信  - 又怎么了？
Dialogue: 1,0:03:06.52,0:03:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}刚才我母亲打来电话 她刚飞到本市 马上就来这里
Dialogue: 1,0:03:11.28,0:03:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}真的假的 我们终于要见到她老人家了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:13.41,0:03:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}- 这可真奇怪  - 奇怪你还有个妈？
Dialogue: 1,0:03:18.45,0:03:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}不是
Dialogue: 1,0:03:20.00,0:03:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}奇怪你妈还想得起来探望你
Dialogue: 1,0:03:23.29,0:03:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}不是！我奇怪她竟要到这里来
Dialogue: 1,0:03:26.00,0:03:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}我一直以为她打死都不会到这种地方来
Dialogue: 1,0:03:29.42,0:03:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}我们这里太低贱还是怎么的？
Dialogue: 1,0:03:32.05,0:03:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}不到一个小时之前 我刚泡过澡（亦有破产之意）
Dialogue: 1,0:03:36.43,0:03:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}你们想太多了 别多心
Dialogue: 1,0:03:39.76,0:03:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}- 只是我妈妈不喜欢酒吧而已\N- 酒吧其实是个挺可悲的地方
Dialogue: 1,0:03:44.56,0:03:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}有些人一辈子都泡在这里
Dialogue: 1,0:03:47.48,0:03:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}就在昨天 有个家伙坐在我旁边足足呆了11个钟头
Dialogue: 1,0:03:56.78,0:04:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}- 这是什么悲催的人生啊 - 太可怜了
Dialogue: 1,0:04:00.62,0:04:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}更可悲的是 他现在可能还在某个酒吧
Dialogue: 1,0:04:03.96,0:04:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}喝着一杯啤酒 吊儿郎当地无所事事
Dialogue: 1,0:04:08.25,0:04:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}黛安 你妈妈但凡有一点像你\N所有人都会喜欢她的
Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.21,0:04:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}她和我一点也不像
Dialogue: 1,0:04:14.05,0:04:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}她人很古怪 有时候很难伺候
Dialogue: 1,0:04:17.76,0:04:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}没错 真是天壤之别
Dialogue: 1,0:04:23.06,0:04:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}黛安 如果令堂很有钱 为啥你这么穷呢？
Dialogue: 1,0:04:28.90,0:04:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}我不想要她的钱\N我不想过那种用银盘子讨钱的生活
Dialogue: 1,0:04:34.95,0:04:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}赏你的
Dialogue: 1,0:04:38.28,0:04:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}谢谢打赏！
Dialogue: 1,0:04:43.50,0:04:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}女儿你在这里呀 我的小宝贝
Dialogue: 1,0:04:46.16,0:04:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}妈咪！
Dialogue: 1,0:04:49.96,0:04:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}闺女
Dialogue: 1,0:04:55.80,0:05:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}她们亲吻都不碰的 谁会连黛安的嘴都瞄不准？
Dialogue: 1,0:05:01.56,0:05:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}原来酒吧长这样啊
Dialogue: 1,0:05:05.56,0:05:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}是的 这就是女儿工作的地方
Dialogue: 1,0:05:10.77,0:05:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}允许我介绍一下 这位是山姆
Dialogue: 1,0:05:13.82,0:05:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}他不会说任何怪话令你女儿难堪\N所以明智地沉默不语
Dialogue: 1,0:05:18.49,0:05:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}幸会
Dialogue: 1,0:05:20.12,0:05:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}嗨
Dialogue: 1,0:05:21.95,0:05:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}这位是卡拉托泰立\N她的话比山姆还少 而且忙得不可开交
Dialogue: 1,0:05:26.75,0:05:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}那边是诺曼和他的好友克里夫
Dialogue: 1,0:05:29.88,0:05:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}他们都在战争中失去了舌头
Dialogue: 1,0:05:34.80,0:05:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}厄尼潘图索 你可以叫他"教练"
Dialogue: 1,0:05:37.72,0:05:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}- 叫我另一个绰号"老红"也行  - "老红"？
Dialogue: 1,0:05:40.76,0:05:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}他做棒球员的时候 他的队友都叫他"老红"
Dialogue: 1,0:05:43.68,0:05:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}因为你的头发是红色的？
Dialogue: 1,0:05:46.02,0:05:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}不 夫人 因为我读过一本红皮的书
Dialogue: 1,0:05:52.31,0:05:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}他人特别好 真的特别好
Dialogue: 1,0:05:55.11,0:05:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}非常高兴 终于见到您了 钱太太
Dialogue: 1,0:05:58.11,0:06:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}见到你我也很高兴 山姆\N黛安说过很多你的事
Dialogue: 1,0:06:02.32,0:06:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}你长得差不多和黛安说你自己认为的那样英俊
Dialogue: 1,0:06:10.46,0:06:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}我尽量把它当成一种恭维
Dialogue: 1,0:06:13.88,0:06:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}您大老远地跑来看我真是太好了
Dialogue: 1,0:06:16.59,0:06:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}我也这样认为 你知道明天是什么日子？
Dialogue: 1,0:06:20.68,0:06:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}- 不知道 什么日子？ - 你明天结婚 恭喜你了
Dialogue: 1,0:06:27.77,0:06:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}我明天什么？
Dialogue: 1,0:06:29.10,0:06:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}如果你过了明天还不结婚
Dialogue: 1,0:06:31.73,0:06:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}我会失去你父亲留给我的那份遗产
Dialogue: 1,0:06:34.31,0:06:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}天啊！怎么会？
Dialogue: 1,0:06:36.73,0:06:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}闺女啊 他死的时候 你还是一个笨拙的小姑娘
Dialogue: 1,0:06:41.20,0:06:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}脑袋总扎在书本里 还有严重的面部痉挛毛病
Dialogue: 1,0:06:46.95,0:06:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}你父亲很担心你永远找不到另一半
Dialogue: 1,0:06:52.87,0:06:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}只能落得个孤独终老
Dialogue: 1,0:06:55.17,0:06:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}所以他要我保证 一定把你给嫁出去
Dialogue: 1,0:06:59.97,0:07:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}必须在他去世十年之内完成
Dialogue: 1,0:07:03.72,0:07:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}他甚至把这一条写进了遗嘱
Dialogue: 1,0:07:05.35,0:07:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}所以 如果你还是单身的话 我就完蛋了
Dialogue: 1,0:07:09.47,0:07:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}你为什么现在才跟我讲？父亲已经去世十年了
Dialogue: 1,0:07:13.19,0:07:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}你知道时间过得有多快 何况你妈又有...
